174 A.3d 517 KEVIN ALEXANDER, APPELLANT-PETITIONER, v. NEW JERSEY DEPARTMENT OF CORRECTIONS, RESPONDENT-RESPONDENT.

C-143 September Term 2017

079491 October 16, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002081-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
